Package com.googlecode.cqengine.quantizer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Quantizer<A>
    A Quantizer converts a fine-grained or continuous value to a discrete or coarse-grained value.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BigDecimalQuantizer
    A static factory for creating Quantizers for BigDecimal attributes.
    BigIntegerQuantizer
    A static factory for creating Quantizers for BigInteger attributes.
    DoubleQuantizer
    A static factory for creating Quantizers for Double attributes.
    FloatQuantizer
    A static factory for creating Quantizers for Float attributes.
    IntegerQuantizer
    A static factory for creating Quantizers for Integer attributes.
    LongQuantizer
    A static factory for creating Quantizers for Long attributes.
